reviewText: Not what I expected. Basic stuff at best

Mama's retouching actions are absolutely superb in every way! They are super easy to use,speed your productivity, and produce STUNNING results. You absolutely cannot go wrong in purchasing these actions. By far the most superior set of actions on the market. Without these actions my workflow would slow to a crawl. Shan Canfield, aka Photoshop Mama is a super talented and extremely knowlegeable Photoshop power user. She passes her love of Photoshop to everyone. You just gotta check out her amazing videos on youtube! Photoshop Mama, you are my HERO! Pam
